description:
Another quick video, this time looking at PragerU, a channel I had always told myself I would never bother with. Well, here we are, trapped in a pandemic and me unable to get my exciting big videos out any quicker. So I guess it's PragerU time.

Here's a fun fact: The working title for this video was "PragerU vid I guess".

This video's structure is a bit weird, and I think my overall message is muddled. That said, it's a fun ride, and maybe some people will enjoy it. There is a dad joke in the cold open though, so fair warning if you're someone who reads the description before watching the video.


Thanks to Pop Arena for providing some voice work for this video! You can see his channel here: https://www.youtube.com/user/poparena


Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/JoseNotAJay 

Contribute to my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/JoseOnYoutube
